        <h2>Check That Your Form Is Correct With Personalized Advice</h2> 
        <p class="pagetext">Spot me’s goal is to be used during a workout. With that in mind, it has a built in Set Feature. This allows you to complete your exercise, and then go back and analyze your skeletal positions for each rep, including the advice from Spot Me on how to improve your form. Or if you want to experiment and see what is good or bad form, use the continuous mode for a continuous analysis of your skeleton.</p>
